-size:12pt">: </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Indeed</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">and </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">I think the response to the Silk Commission very much confirmed what the Secretary of State has just said.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Chair:</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">We are coming to a close, bu</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">t I am quickly looking </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">round to see if anyone has any final questions for the Ministers while they are in front of us. Nobody seems to be catching my eye.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Q437 </span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Nia</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> Griffith:</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">I have one question about time scale. When does the Secretary of State think that he will be bringing forward the actual Bill itself?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Mr Jones</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">: </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Clearly, a lot depends upon the work of this Committee</sp